                <note rend="inline" type="source">823.51/190: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Peru</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Gonzales</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1921-09-22T18:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 22, 1921—6 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>48. Your 70, September 20, noon.</p>
                <p>General conditions outlined satisfactory to Dr. Cumberland. Please cable whether
                    Peruvian Ambassador will be empowered by cable to discuss details and sign
                    contract.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
